<tr><td align="left" class="newsCategory">GeneralNews - <font align="left" class="newsDate">6:45 AM PST</font></td></tr>
<tr><td valign="top" class="newsText">From the EQ Patcher:<br><br><blockquote>December 23, 2003 <br>------------------------------ <br>** Stability Issues ** <br><br>The team here at the EQ Lab has isolated a memory leak which was causing server instability after 10 to 12 hours of uptime (which we are sure you have noticed) We hope to have this issue resolved during tonight's update. We would like to thank you all for your patience and understanding during these last few trying days and wish you the best of luck this holiday season. <br><br>Thanks for your time and thank you for being a part of Norrath.</blockquote>Hopefully it'll be fixed by now!<br></td></tr>
