<tr><td align="left" class="newsCategory">GeneralNews - <font align="left" class="newsDate">5:09 PM PST</font></td></tr>
<tr><td valign="top" class="newsText">If you're looking for that perfect gift for your favorite EQ player...<br><br><blockquote>For a limited time, gift your fellow players with additional 30, 60 and 90 day subscription time for EverQuest, EverQuest Online Adventures or PlanetSide.<br><br>You can also gift them with a digital download of an EverQuest expansion pack or PlanetSide: Core Combat.<br><br>Show that special friend how much he or she makes your gaming more fun!<br><br>Click here for details:<br><br><a href="https://store.station.sony.com/gift/index.jsp">https://store.station.sony.com/gift/index.jsp</a></blockquote>Enjoy!<br><br></td></tr>
