<tr><td valign="top" class="newsText">GamesGuidesOnline and Stratics have teamed up to bring a special offer to all Stratics Plus members, a free guide!<br><br>You can register for the free guide on platinum money-making tips for characters of all levels <a href="http://www.gameguidesonline.com/GGO/signup/register.asp">Right Here!</a><br><br>The site offers a wide variety of guides for almost anything you could wish for in the game of EverQuest, and others as well.<br><br>At the same time as providing this comprehensive listing of guides they offer full support and daily updates on their message boards located at <a href="http://www.guidenation.com/">http://www.guidenation.com/</a><br><br>So if you've been looking for something to give you that extra edge, go check it out!</td></tr>
