<tr><td valign="top" class="newsText">From the Dev Corner:<br><br><blockquote>The server formerly known as "The Fallen" has had it's name changed to "Discord".  Market research, including several studies by the renowned Server Names for a Better Norrath, has pointed out that the previous name provoked memories of the once rampant falls for 10k Damage in EverQuest.  The new name, research shows, will more aptly promote the expected environment on the server of rampant Chaos.<br> <br>Thanks for your time and be sure to try out "The Fallen!"  Err DISCORD!</blockquote>Same server, different name!  <br><br>What do you think of its prospects so far?</td></tr>
