<tr><td align="left" class="newsCategory">Stratics Network Announcement - <font align="left" class="newsDate">8:23 AM PST</font></td></tr>
<tr><td valign="top" class="newsText"><a href="http://swg.stratics.com">SWG Stratics</a> is pleased to announce this month's House of Commons chat with the Dev Team of Star Wars Galaxies! <i>Vehicles &amp; Jedi</i> will be the primary topics of concern, and the Dev Team will be waiting on Stratics IRC this Thursday in order to answer your questions.<p><b>The SWGHoC will be held Thursday, December 18th at 5:00 PM Pacific Time, in #swghoc on Stratics IRC.</b><p>In order to connect to Stratics IRC, please log onto to one of the following servers using your favorite IRC client:<ul><li>irc.stratics.com, port 6667 (connects to a random server on our network)</li><li>irc.frws.com, port 6667 (USA, Colorado)</li><li>irc.epaxsys.net, ports 6667, 6668, 7000 (USA, Colorado)</li><li>irc.glowfish.de, ports 6667, 6668, 7000 (EU, Germany)</li><li>stratics.afraidyet.net, port 6667 (USA, Georgia)</li></ul>Once you've logged on, type /join #swghoc. In case of difficulties, please visit <a href="http://chat.stratics.com">chat.stratics.com</a> for more information on <a href="http://chat.stratics.com/content/community/connect.shtml">how to connect to the chat</a>. As an alternative, you can also use our web-based <a href="http://chat.stratics.com/content/java/800chat.shtml">Java IRC Client</a>.<p>If you'd like to chat with other players before, during or after the SWGHoC, please visit our official SWGS chat channel, <a href="irc://irc.stratics.com:6667/starwars">#starwars</a>, which is open for discussion 24/7, 365. :)</td></tr>
