<tr><td valign="top" class="newsText">It's finally time for our 7th Community Chat with the World of Warcraft community! Like with the  <a href="http://wow.stratics.com/content/communication/irc/transcript/index.shtml" target="_blank" >previous events</a> we invite everyone from the World of Warcraft community to join us in our IRC channel for some live discussion over some selected topics.<br><br><b>Date:</b> December 12th. (Friday)<br><b>Time:</b> 6 PM EST, Midnight CET.<br><b>Server:</b> irc.stratics.com<br><b>Channel:</b> #worldofwarcraft<br><br>For more information about Stratics IRC, visit <a href="http://chat.stratics.com/" target="_blank" >this page</a>.<br><br>If you have suggestions for discussion topics, don't hesitate to <a href="mailto:wownews@stratics.com">email us</a>!</td></tr>
